sdf:title: OMA LwM2M Analog Output (Object ID 3203)
title: Analog Output
description: This IPSO object is a generic object that can be used with any kind of analog output interface.

Analog_Output_Current_Value.title: Analog Output Current Value
Analog_Output_Current_Value.description: The current value of the analog output.

Application_Type.title: Application Type
Application_Type.description: The application type of the sensor or actuator as a string depending on the use case.

Min_Range_Value.title: Min Range Value
Min_Range_Value.description: The minimum value that can be measured by the sensor.

Max_Range_Value.title: Max Range Value
Max_Range_Value.description: The maximum value that can be measured by the sensor.

Timestamp.title: Timestamp
Timestamp.description: The timestamp of when the measurement was performed.

Fractional_Timestamp.title: Fractional Timestamp
Fractional_Timestamp.description: Fractional part of the timestamp when sub-second precision is used (e.g., 0.23 for 230 ms).
